<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Compte vérifié · EchoCare</title>
    <style>
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
            background: #F0E6D8;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }
        .card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 50px 40px;
            max-width: 480px;
            width: 100%;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .icon { font-size: 70px; margin-bottom: 20px; animation: pop 0.5s ease; }
        @keyframes pop {
            0% { transform: scale(0); }
            80% { transform: scale(1.2); }
            100% { transform: scale(1); }
        }
        h2 { color: #27ae60; font-size: 26px; margin-bottom: 12px; }
        p { color: #777; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 10px; }
        .countdown { color: #4A6FA5; font-weight: 700; font-size: 16px; margin: 16px 0; }
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 10px;
            padding: 14px 32px;
            background: #E8895A;
            color: white;
            border-radius: 10px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 15px;
            transition: background 0.2s;
        }
        .btn:hover { background: #d4784a; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="card">
    <div class="icon">✅</div>
    <h2>Compte vérifié !</h2>
    <p>Votre compte a été activé avec succès.</p>
    <p>Vous allez être redirigé automatiquement dans :</p>
    <div class="countdown"><span id="count">5</span> secondes...</div>
    <a href="{{ path('app_login') }}" class="btn">Se connecter maintenant</a>
</div>

<script>
    let count = 5;
    const el = document.getElementById('count');
    const interval = setInterval(() => {
        count--;
        el.textContent = count;
        if (count <= 0) {
            clearInterval(interval);
            window.location.href = "{{ path('app_login') }}";
        }
    }, 1000);
</script>
</body>
</html>